@startuml component
title Tic-Tac-Toe — Component Architecture

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor Player

package "src/" {
  [main.ts\n(entry)] as main
  [TicTacToe\n(pure logic, TS)] as game
  [ui.ts\n(DOM bindings)] as ui
  [styles.css] as css
}

cloud "DOM\n(#app)" as dom

Player --> dom : click / keyboard
dom --> ui : event handlers
ui --> game : play(cell), reset(), board, status
game --> ui : returns Result + Status
ui --> dom : re-render squares + message + win line

main --> game : new TicTacToe()
main --> ui : mount(root, game)
main --> dom : exposes window.__ttt for e2e

note right of game
  Discriminated-union Status:
    {kind:"in-progress", currentPlayer}
    {kind:"won", winner, line}
    {kind:"tie"}
  No DOM access.
end note
@enduml
